OL,3,C'Are they going to die?' Ammanford
OL,4,Cstab attack pupil asked police
OL,6,FA teenage girl accused of the
OL,7,Fattempted murder of two teachers and a
OL,8,Fpupil during a school stabbing asked
OL,9,Fpolice if her victims were going to
OL,10,Fdie, a court has heard.
OL,12,FTeachers Fiona Elias and Liz Hopkin
OL,13,Fsustained multiple injuries in the
OL,14,Fattack at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman. A year
OL,15,F10 pupil was also stabbed in the
OL,16,Fincident which threw the school into
OL,17,Flockdown in April last year.
