OL,6,FThe 14-year-old defendant denies three
OL,7,Fcounts of attempted murder. The girl
OL,8,Fhad previously pleaded guilty to three
OL,9,Fcounts of wounding with intent and a
OL,10,Fcharge of possessing a bladed article
OL,11,Fon school premises.
OL,13,FToday a jury was played body-worn
OL,14,Ffootage of the teenage girl's arrest
OL,15,Fcaptured by an officer who sat in the
OL,16,Fback of a police vehicle with the
OL,17,Fdefendant.
