OL,3,C'Are they going to die?' Ammanford
OL,4,Cstab attack pupil asked police
OL,6,FDuring the journey from the school,
OL,7,Fthe teenage girl asks the officer if
OL,8,Fshe knows the pupil who had been
OL,9,Fstabbed.JWhen the officer replied no
OL,10,Fthe girl said, "I stabbed
OL,11,Fher...oopsie."
OL,13,FThe court heard the footage also
OL,14,Fcaptured an exchange between the
OL,15,Fofficer and the defendant in which the
OL,16,Fteenage girl said she was likely to be
OL,17,Fon the news.
OL,19,FThe officer told the girl, "Sorry, you
OL,20,Fare going to have to deal with me
OL,21,Fstaring at you."
