OL,3,C'Are they going to die?' Ammanford
OL,4,Cstab attack pupil asked police
OL,6,FThe girl replied, "It's fine I've had
OL,7,Floads of eyes on me today. Sooner or
OL,8,Flater, I'm ninety per cent sure this
OL,9,Fis going to be on the news, so even
OL,10,Fmore eyes will be on me."
OL,12,FLater in the recording, the vehicle is
OL,13,Fseen parked at a police station.
OL,15,FThe girl asks, "How am I going to face
OL,16,Fmy family after what I have done?"
OL,17,FWith the officer replying, "I can't
OL,18,Fanswer that one for you."
OL,20,FThe defendant then says, "That's if
OL,21,Fthey even show up."
